placeData.name: Seattle Meowtropolitan

coverImg.alt: Cup of latte with cat latte foam art.

placeData.desc: Come stop by Seattle Meowtropolitan to play with cats while sipping on some coffee andsnacking on some pastries. Reservations are recommended but walk-ins are welcomed.

placeData.name: Twice Sold Tales

coverImg.alt: Cat laying down next to a bookshelf inside of Twice Sold Tales, a second-hand bookstore.

placeData.desc: Search through the numerous second-hand books at this bookstore. Maybe while you're searching for your next read, you'll run into one of the live-in kitties!

placeData.name: Rubber Chicken Museum

coverImg.alt: Rubber chickens inside a display case.

placeData.desc: Located in the back of a novelty store in Wallingford is the rubber chicken museum. It boasts a surprisingly large number of rubber chickens. Entrance to the museum is free!

placeData.name: Archie McPhee

coverImg.alt: A 2d cartoon cutout of a alien baby-esque cartoon holding a bulb with a human head. The cartoon is plastered on the outside wall of Archie Mcphee, a novelty store.

placeData.desc: A novelty store located in Wallingford. Home to the Rubber Duck Museum and the Wallingford Beast.

reviewData.desc: I came with my friend and we had made a reservation before hand. We arrived about 10 minutes early and decided to get some coffee. I got a 12oz latte and was very surprised at the cute cat latte art the barista had made! My friend got an americano, so no latte art for him. About 5 minutes before our reservation, one of the staff came out and gave us a rundown on some rules to make sure we can enjoy our time with the cats to the fullest. The cats were adorable and really liked my friend, he had 3 of them playing with him at one point. We would totally come by again!

imgs.alt: Cup of latte with cat latte foam art.
Cup of latte with latte foam art of a cat's head in shape of a heart.
Cat themed earrings for sale hanging off a jewelry display.

reviewData.desc: Super cute cats. I thought I was going to get bored midway but time passed by faster than I thought it would.
